本表所列年岁为虚拟数字。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1091&endYear=1108')\">1091-1108年</a>，居乡？<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9da387f81e6646a9aa55255e3d7f93ae\");'><span id='9da387f81e6646a9aa55255e3d7f93ae_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1114')\">1109-1114年</a>，19-24岁</div><div id='9da387f81e6646a9aa55255e3d7f93ae' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1109&endYear=1109')\">1109年</a>，在太学？<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1110&endYear=1110')\">1110年</a>，在太学，时乃父因言事落职，为父抗章申冤，由是知名。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1111&endYear=1114')\">1111-1114年</a>，在太学？<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ce778f4fb97c466490b993affdb0ebb4\");'><span id='ce778f4fb97c466490b993affdb0ebb4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，36岁</div><div id='ce778f4fb97c466490b993affdb0ebb4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年1月30日</a>，应召进行京任京畿提刑，上书御史中丞何栗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年6月</a>，入李纲帅幕出兵救太原。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.037723,"Longitude":111.704994,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4307","Title":"常德","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ea41657b48724cfcb46bdab867211faa\");'><span id='ea41657b48724cfcb46bdab867211faa_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1115&endYear=1122')\">1115-1122年</a>，25-32岁</div><div id='ea41657b48724cfcb46bdab867211faa' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1115&endYear=1118')\">1115-1118年</a>，佐鼎澧帅幕？<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1119&endYear=1119')\">1119年</a>，佐鼎澧帅幕，尝遇“溪蛮啸聚”，“单骑入贼巢、羁致其酋”<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1120&endYear=1120')\">1120年</a>，佐鼎澧帅幕？<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1121&endYear=1121')\">1121年4月4日</a>，由成忠郎换文资为从事郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1122&endYear=1122')\">1122年</a>，佐鼎澧帅幕？<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"661c5bbb37cf484391706dc4bcc13ed7\");'><span id='661c5bbb37cf484391706dc4bcc13ed7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1129')\">1127-1129年</a>，37-39岁</div><div id='661c5bbb37cf484391706dc4bcc13ed7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年6月4日</a>，李纲拜相，命以宁为枢密院编修官知鼎州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年</a>，知鼎州（后改名常德府）。李纲罢相贬居鄂州，过鼎州药山时以宁与之游。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，以知鼎州辟为川陕宣抚处置使张浚参议官。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.278131,"Longitude":119.190904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN321081","Title":"仪征","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"036a6df224ce4b13beffe65425757fc5\");'><span id='036a6df224ce4b13beffe65425757fc5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1124')\">1123-1124年</a>，33-34岁</div><div id='036a6df224ce4b13beffe65425757fc5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1123&endYear=1124')\">1123-1124年</a>，为江淮发运司管勾文字。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.017144,"Longitude":118.55143,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN320830","Title":"盱眙","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"aa5ebb7d903b43b49963e9e0f2906293\");'><span id='aa5ebb7d903b43b49963e9e0f2906293_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1125&endYear=1125')\">1125年</a>，35岁</div><div id='aa5ebb7d903b43b49963e9e0f2906293' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1125&endYear=1125')\">1125年</a>，曾赴泗州，夜宿龟山，登秋汉亭，有词。<span class='label'>作品：</span>虞美人（归来峰下霜如水）<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">虞美人 宿龟山夜登秋汉亭（宋·王以宁）</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->归来峰下霜如水。明月三千里。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->幽人独立瞰长淮。谁棹扁舟一叶、趁潮来。<!--E--></p><div class='small'></div><p><!--S-->洞庭湖上银涛观。忆我烟蓑伴。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->此身天地一浮萍。去国十年华发、欲星星。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":37.27111,"Longitude":111.794367,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN141182","Title":"汾阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e4a0e2e5c0f9421bbb327c34ef54cfda\");'><span id='e4a0e2e5c0f9421bbb327c34ef54cfda_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年</a>，36岁</div><div id='e4a0e2e5c0f9421bbb327c34ef54cfda' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年7月</a>，屯兵汾州，督战过文水，兵败。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.251769,"Longitude":113.087489,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN430121","Title":"长沙","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"db5df968eb474c95bffc505e56f26ae2\");'><span id='db5df968eb474c95bffc505e56f26ae2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1127')\">1126-1127年</a>，36-37岁</div><div id='db5df968eb474c95bffc505e56f26ae2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年9月</a>，居长沙，有词怀古。<span class='label'>作品：</span>水调歌头（岁晚橘洲上）<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">水调歌头 其一 裴公亭怀古（宋·王以宁）</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->岁晚橘洲上，老叶舞愁红。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->西山光翠，依旧影落酒杯中。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->人在子亭高处，下望长沙城郭，猎猎酒帘风。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->远水湛寒碧，独钓绿蓑翁。<!--E--></p><div class='small'></div><p><!--S-->怀往事，追昨梦，转头空。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->孙郎前日，豪健颐指五都雄。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->起拥奇才剑客，十万银戈赤帻，歌鼓壮军容。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->何似裴相国，谈道老圭峰。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1126&endYear=1126')\">1126年9月</a>，居长沙，有词。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1127&endYear=1127')\">1127年4月</a>，在长沙翠蔼堂与贬谪滞留此地的李纲相遇，李纲书杜诗赠之。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"901328edf80749f8a6685538446cfdbd\");'><span id='901328edf80749f8a6685538446cfdbd_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，40岁</div><div id='901328edf80749f8a6685538446cfdbd' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年8月</a>，屯兵潭州，为“游寇”孔彦舟所败，亡去。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f396e66e1e6e433d846745ac2f5062b2\");'><span id='f396e66e1e6e433d846745ac2f5062b2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，40岁</div><div id='f396e66e1e6e433d846745ac2f5062b2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年12月</a>，在长沙，曾遣人献马四匹于朝。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.014789,"Longitude":112.129089,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4206","Title":"襄阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9f82159d1450462d82ff5755e5e45c32\");'><span id='9f82159d1450462d82ff5755e5e45c32_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，40岁</div><div id='9f82159d1450462d82ff5755e5e45c32' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年3月</a>，转战两湖。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.694085,"Longitude":112.093781,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN411381","Title":"邓州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9cbb9f7daa834f69ae07acb4dabe3d50\");'><span id='9cbb9f7daa834f69ae07acb4dabe3d50_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，40岁</div><div id='9cbb9f7daa834f69ae07acb4dabe3d50' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年7月</a>，转战至邓州，席上赋词。<span class='label'>作品：</span>满庭芳（千古南阳）<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">满庭芳 其二 邓州席上（宋·王以宁）</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->千古南阳，刘郎乡国，依约楚俗秦风。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->英姿豪气，耆旧笑谈中。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->珰佩来从帝所，许洲花、潭菊从容。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->霜秋晓，凉生日观，极目送飞鸿。<!--E--></p><div class='small'></div><p><!--S-->主公。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->天下士，挥毫万字，一饮千钟。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->醉高歌起舞，唤醒人龙。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->我自人间漫浪，平生事、南北西东。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->辞公去，寒眸激电，曾识小安丰。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.459422,"Longitude":114.878872,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4211","Title":"黄冈","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8df04cb586994cb4b29070fd6b0799a0\");'><span id='8df04cb586994cb4b29070fd6b0799a0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，40岁</div><div id='8df04cb586994cb4b29070fd6b0799a0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年9月</a>，至黄州，重午登栖霞楼，作词抒怀。<span class='label'>作品：</span>满庭芳（千古黄州）<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">满庭芳 其四 重午登霞楼（宋·王以宁）<br />　　押豪韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->千古黄州，雪堂奇胜，名与赤壁齐高。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->竹楼千字，笔势压江涛。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->笑问江头皓月，应曾照、今古英豪。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->菖蒲酒，窊尊无恙，聊共访临皋。<!--E--></p><div class='small'></div><p><!--S-->陶陶。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->谁晤对，粲花吐论，宫锦纫袍。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->借银涛雪浪，一洗尘劳。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->好在江山如画，人易老、双鬓难薅。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->升平代，凭高望远，当赋反离骚。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":29.363262,"Longitude":113.135679,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4306","Title":"岳阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4c4244bad885450bb696d388a89f6ca9\");'><span id='4c4244bad885450bb696d388a89f6ca9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，40岁</div><div id='4c4244bad885450bb696d388a89f6ca9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，与画家任才仲交游唱和，有词。<span class='label'>作品：</span>感皇恩（千古洞庭湖）<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">感皇恩 和才仲西山子（宋·王以宁）</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->千古洞庭湖，百川争注。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->雪浪银涛正如许。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->骑鲸诗客，浩气决云飞雾。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->背人歌欸乃，凌空去。<!--E--></p><div class='small'></div><p><!--S-->我欲从公，翩然鹄举。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->未愿人间相君雨。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->笭箵短棹，是我平生真语。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->个中烟景好，烦公句。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.662297,"Longitude":121.426996,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN331","Title":"台州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"09ca8b2364df427bbfe03710bdd36e56\");'><span id='09ca8b2364df427bbfe03710bdd36e56_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1133')\">1131-1133年</a>，41-43岁</div><div id='09ca8b2364df427bbfe03710bdd36e56' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1131')\">1131年1月</a>，因遭言者弹劾落职，责监台州酒务。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年9月</a>，再贬永州别驾、潮州安置。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1132')\">1132年12月7日</a>，在台州皈依佛教，自号正信居士，有文纪事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>佛窟山转轮藏记。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年2月21日</a>，在台州，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>广平夫人往生记。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":23.662923,"Longitude":116.62943,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4451","Title":"潮州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"00209f751aa74079adc448ac54708f75\");'><span id='00209f751aa74079adc448ac54708f75_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1135')\">1133-1135年</a>，43-45岁</div><div id='00209f751aa74079adc448ac54708f75' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1133&endYear=1133')\">1133年</a>，谪居潮州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1134&endYear=1134')\">1134年3月1日</a>，谪居潮州，三月初一撰铭文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>马王庙钟款。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1135&endYear=1135')\">1135年</a>，特许自便，遂离潮州回鼎州省母。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":26.080447,"Longitude":119.302938,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3501","Title":"福州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9ed112cce07c49ba9df7fc75a4b5e2bd\");'><span id='9ed112cce07c49ba9df7fc75a4b5e2bd_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1135&endYear=1135')\">1135年</a>，45岁</div><div id='9ed112cce07c49ba9df7fc75a4b5e2bd' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1135&endYear=1135')\">1135年</a>，秋日过福州，遇张元干、刘子翚。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.283713,"Longitude":112.558237,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN430124","Title":"宁乡","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2ec9e03b184a4ba5b98a778ba8f438e9\");'><span id='2ec9e03b184a4ba5b98a778ba8f438e9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1139')\">1136-1139年</a>，46-49岁</div><div id='2ec9e03b184a4ba5b98a778ba8f438e9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1136&endYear=1139')\">1136-1139年</a>，居乡。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":25.934353,"Longitude":111.079609,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN450324","Title":"全州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"38cbb5eb2fd44c20b982aa5381489252\");'><span id='38cbb5eb2fd44c20b982aa5381489252_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1142')\">1140-1142年</a>，50-52岁</div><div id='38cbb5eb2fd44c20b982aa5381489252' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1140')\">1140年</a>，复右朝奉郎知全州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1141&endYear=1142')\">1141-1142年</a>，知全州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.461662,"Longitude":114.89864,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4211 栖霞楼","Title":"栖霞楼"},{"Latitude":29.388217,"Longitude":113.099526,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4306 岳阳楼","Title":"岳阳楼"}],"Title":"王以宁 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1090-1146)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：王兆鹏等《两宋词从丛考》、王兆鹏《宋才子传笺证·词人卷》　录入整理：王兆鹏</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 8, 115.447949, 32.55348, 7)\">0-37岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">湘潭</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">常德</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">仪征</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">盱眙</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">汾阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">长沙</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(8, 12, 112.3962415, 30.4